Team sharing some update.
@Akshit Digital Srishti Media's main man Bibhu asked me who will presenting the 3 month media plan to them? I said either you or Padma, then he asked about your profiles thats when I was like LOL. 
Anyway @Preetika drive pressure to sign agreement from morning.



SOW: 
Main client: Ashoka University
Our client: 

1.83 lac monthy
starting date: 15th Sep
Project duration: 3 months
Payment Terms: 50% advance monthly.
Media Commission: 0% Mention that specifically
(This is our counter towards further cost conversations)

Basic Task:
Media Management
Performance Management

Assets provided:
3 films for TOFU
Quiz Lead Gen landing page BOFU

Expectations and Terms:
We just have to get results via targeting and media optimization.
Our SOW does not include web/campaign/creative etc.
We have to procure media from media mix and get results.
We can adjust current plan.

We have to push contract signing before we are pushed to present today for their clients.

They are asking for creds of Akshit and Padma like a lot is on the line here for them and they are presenting an urgency to close with us. 

Other than whats in the client docs which @Akshit Digital and I have been through last evening. 

Here are some details worth noting:
We are only managing 1 CR media as per approved 3 month plan. 
Our date starts from 15th Sep.
We will pitch for them but we will have to be paid 50% in ADVANCE ASAP. Building that pressure to get paid and to know this project is FOR REAL is super important. We can come in 1 meeting, for the next one money has to come through. PERIOD.
Payment of all media amounting to 1 CR will be done by client or the BTL agency
